Package: pppindexr
Title: Price and Quantity Indices for International Comparisons
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Erik Ø.", "Sørensen", , "erik.sorensen@nhh.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7155-4188"))
Description: Calculate the most popular ways to compare real incomes across 
  countries, the Geary-Khamis index (real income at international prices, 
  including the reference price vector), the Eltetö, Köves and Szulc index 
  (EKS), and the multilateral translog price indexes by Caves, Christensen,
  and Diewert (CCD). Also provides helper functions for ordinary price and 
  quantity indices.
